tons to dynamically change the audio playback speed. </p>\n<p>The following code will create a button that will change the audio playback to 0.5 times speed:</p>\n<pre class="brush: xml; title: ; notranslate">\r\n&lt;a href=''#'' onclick=''JavaScript:jQuery(&quot;#wonderpluginaudio-2&quot;).data(&quot;object&quot;).setPlaybackRate(0.5);return false;''&gt;&lt;button&gt;0.5X Speed&lt;/button&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n</pre>\n<p>In the above code, the number <code>2</code> in the <code>wonderpluginaudio-2</code> is the ID of the player. Please make sure to change the number to the ID of your own player.</p>\n<p>The following code will create a button that will change the audio playback to normal speed:</p>\n<pre class="brush: xml; title: ; notranslate">\r\n&lt;a href=''#'' onclick=''JavaScript:jQuery(&quot;#wonderpluginaudio-2&quot;).data(&quot;object&quot;).setPlaybackRate(1);return false;''&gt;&lt;button&gt;1X Speed&lt;/button&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n</pre>\n<p>The following code will create a button that will change the audio playback to 2 times speed:</p>\n<pre class="brush: xml; title: ; notranslate">\r\n&lt;a href=''#'' onclick=''JavaScript:jQuery(&quot;#wonderpluginaudio-2&quot;).data(&quot;object&quot;).setPlaybackRate(2);return false;''&gt;&lt;button&gt;2X Speed&lt;/button&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n</pre>\n<p>An online demo is as follows:</p>\n<style type="text/css">@import url(https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans|Oswald);  #wonderpluginaudio-2 { 	box-sizing: content-box; }  #wonderpluginaudio-2 div { 	-webkit-box-sizing: content-box; 	-moz-box-sizing: content-box; 	box-sizing: content-box;    }  #wonderpluginaudio-2 .amazingaudioplayer-image { 	display: block; 	position: relative; 	float: left; 	margin: 4px; 	overflow: hidden; 	-webkit-box-shadow: 0 8px 6px -6px black; 	-moz-box-shadow: 0 8px 6px -6px black; 	box-shadow: 0 8px 6px -6px black; 	-webkit-border-radius: 4px;     	-moz-border-radius: 4px;     	border-radius: 4px; }  #wonderpluginaudio-2 .amazingaudioplayer-im